<%= json_paged_resource(:payment_method, "user:paymentmethods") %>

You can `GET` the href of this link to retrieve the
[`PaymentMethods`](#paymentmethods) resource that contains the current user's
payment methods. This endpoint requires the `read:user` scope.


### Parameters

| **Name**  **Type** | **Description** |
| `type` | `string` | Filters results to only include payment methods with the specified comma-separated list of types. See [Payment Method Types](#paymentmethodtypes). |


### Response

Returns the [`PaymentMethods`](#paymentmethods) resource that contains current 
user's payment methods.